* Z-Ordering to\nLiquid Clustering Migration
** Z-Order Legacy Technique
***_ OPTIMIZE ... ZORDER BY (cols)
***_ Applied during OPTIMIZE only
***_ Transaction-level concurrency
***_ Changing keys = full rewrite
** Liquid Clustering Advantages
***_ Incremental optimization
***_ Row-level concurrency
***_ Flexible key changes
** Migration Steps
***_ Enable CLUSTER BY on unpartitioned table
***_ Run OPTIMIZE to begin new clustering
***_ Run OPTIMIZE FULL to rewrite existing data
@endmindmap
